### Requirements

- Python 3.9+
- bt_api_base >= 0.15

### Architecture

```
bt_api_mexc/
├── src/bt_api_mexc/     # Source code
│   ├── containers/     # Data containers
│   ├── feeds/          # API feeds
│   ├── gateway/       # Gateway adapter
│   └── plugin.py      # Plugin registration
├── tests/             # Unit tests
└── docs/             # Documentation
```

